fields.title: About Xenia Concerts
fields.mainDescription:
The mission of Xenia Concerts Inc. is to offer high-quality music and arts performances, presentations, and educational programs in an environment that welcomes those who face systemic and social barriers to inclusion at typical arts events.\
\
By reimagining music and arts events and activities to make them inclusive, relevant, and accessible to all members of society, Xenia strives towards improving quality of life and promoting the enjoyment of the arts.

fields.title: George Weston Recital Hall at Meridian Arts Centre
fields.description: George Weston Recital Hall: This theatre space is an aural marvel created by New York acoustician Russell Johnson. It is an acoustically ideal rectangular room with walls meticulously insulated to remove almost all background noise. It can seat 1036 guests.

fields.title: Studio Theatre at Meridian Arts Centre
fields.description: Studio Theatre: The "black box" design of this theatre makes it a versatile performance space for 183 guests. The flexible space is perfect for proscenium-style drama, theatre in the round, experimental formats, and cabaret-style dinner theatre.
